; RawrXD C++ Compiler v1.0 (RXCC)
; Pure MASM64 C++ to x64 PE Compiler - Zero Dependencies
; Finalizes: Lexer, Parser, x64 CodeGen, PE Writer
; =============================================================================

; Assembler: ml64.exe (Microsoft Macro Assembler x64)
; Linker: None required (emits standalone .exe)
; Input: C++ source file (simple subset)
